window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>From the halls of Montezuma...</p> <p>Former Marine Captain Alexander Hale only wanted a weekend out with some old buddies. He could have done without the gang war, the shootout, and...oh yeah, the alien abduction.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p> <p>Now he's in the middle of something he doesn't understand, never asked for, and is having quite possibly the greatest time of his life. Semper Fi and which way are the shores of Tripoli anyway?</p>"; 
